{"questionId":"5965","questionHtml":"<p>A wind turbine has a power output <em>p </em>when the wind speed is <em>v</em>. The efficiency of the wind turbine&nbsp;does not change. What is the wind speed at which the power output is <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{p}{2}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>p</mi>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>?</p>\n<p>A. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{v}{4}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>v</mi>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{v}{{\\sqrt 8 }}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>v</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <msqrt>\n        <mn>8</mn>\n      </msqrt>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{v}{2}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>v</mi>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{v}{{\\sqrt[3]{2}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>v</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mroot>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n      </mroot>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"5965","referenceCode":"18M.1.SL.TZ2.28","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A wind turbine has a power output p when the wind speed is v. The efficiency of the wind turbine does not change. What is the wind speed at which the power output is p 2 ? A. v 4 B","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"28","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 8: Energy production","8.1 – Energy sources","Core","Topic 8: Energy production"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}